theorem
Th21: (for X being non  empty TopSpace holds (for n being (Element of ( NAT )) holds (for p1,p2 being (Point of ( TOP-REAL n )) holds (for f1,f2 being (Function of X,( R^1 )) holds ((f1 is  continuous & f2 is  continuous) implies (ex g being (Function of X,( TOP-REAL n )) st ((for r being (Point of X) holds ( g . r ) = ( ( ( f1 . r ) * p1 ) + ( ( f2 . r ) * p2 ) )) & g is  continuous)))))))
