proof
let r being (Point of X);
( g . r ) = ( ( g1 . r ) + ( g2 . r ) ) by A7;
then ( g . r ) = ( ( g1 . r ) + ( ( f2 . r ) * p2 ) ) by A5;
hence thesis by A3;
end;
hence thesis by A8;
